div.div: split up input file into smaller chunks for parallel processing

1. get input document from s3 input bucket
2. split up into records
3. put records as pending into s3 work bucket
4. trigger record processing via sqs message into process-queue

div.div: process chunks of records in parallel and detect if all records have been processed
1. get pending records data from s3 work bucket

2. process the pending record
3. write result of record processing back to s3
4. delete file of pending record
5. check if batch is complete
6. send completion message to completion-queue
